# 世维会代表出席大众汽车股东会　吁关闭新疆工厂

Author: None

Publisher: Radio Free Asia (Organization)

Published Time: 2023-05-10T15:27:00-04:00

Modified Time: 2023-05-11T10:01:26-04:00

